Game Notes

Sphinx and The Cursed Mummy is an original 3rd person action-adventure
inspired by the mythology of ancient Egypt. Travelling the world via magical
portals to foil the evil plans of Set. Sphinx's Journey will require all his
wits, agility, and special powers. He will also rely on his reluctant hero
friend, The Mummy, to help when being inconspicuous is the only solution

Install Notes

1. Extract RARs
2. Install the game
3. Have fun!
